        section.introduction
            .container
                .row
                    .col-12
                        h2 A Brief Overview and Location

                        p The Westin Los Cabos Resort Villas - Baja Point is an oceanfront vacation resort located along the stunning coastline of Los Cabos, in San José del Cabo, Baja California Sur, Mexico. Nestled on the Tourist Corridor at Carretera Transpeninsular km 22.5, this property offers direct views of the Sea of Cortez and Pacific Ocean, combining the natural beauty of the Baja Peninsula with upscale amenities and services. The resort is approximately 16 km from Los Cabos International Airport, making it easily accessible for travelers arriving by air.
                        p Designed with spacious villa-style accommodations featuring fully equipped kitchens, private balconies, and generous living areas, the resort caters to families, couples, and groups seeking comfort and coastal relaxation. Many units boast panoramic or partial ocean views, adding to the serene atmosphere of this seaside destination.

        section.features
            .container
                .row
                    .col-12
                        h3 The Resort’s Strong Points
                        p Spectacular Location and Views
                        p The resort’s prime position overlooking the Sea of Cortez places guests directly on a scenic stretch of coastline, offering dramatic ocean vistas and easy access to a private beach area. Whether you’re enjoying sunset views from your balcony or relaxing by the water, the location provides an ideal setting for a beachfront getaway.

                        p Spacious and Comfortable Villas
                        p Accommodations at the resort are designed for comfort and convenience, with one-, two-, or three-bedroom villas equipped with home-like amenities such as full kitchens, washers/dryers, living areas, and complimentary Wi-Fi. Most villas offer ocean views and large balconies, perfect for unwinding after a day of activities.

                        p Diverse On-Site Dining Options
                        p Guests can enjoy a range of culinary experiences without leaving the property. The resort features multiple restaurants and bars serving everything from modern Mexican cuisine to casual poolside snacks and seasonal specialties. Whether dining al fresco overlooking the ocean or grabbing a drink at the swim-up bar, there’s something for every palate.

                        p World-Class Amenities and Activities
                        p The resort offers a wide array of amenities, including an infinity pool with a swim-up bar, spa services, fitness facilities, tennis courts, and a kids club for younger travelers. Concierge services can help arrange local excursions, golf outings, or visits to iconic nearby sites like the Arch of Cabo San Lucas.

                        p Family-Friendly Features
                        p From on-site kids clubs and outdoor pools to beach yoga and nearby water sports, the resort provides fun and engaging activities for guests of all ages. Additionally, family-oriented facilities and services make it a strong choice for travelers with children.

                        p Excellent Reviews and Guest Satisfaction
                        p Travelers consistently note the resort’s scenic oceanfront setting, spacious accommodations, and attentive service. Many guests highlight the stunning views, relaxing atmosphere, and comprehensive amenities as key reasons they enjoyed their stay.

